Here is every feature PSRP has to offer:

-------------
POLICE SYSTEM
-------------

Get pulled over by law enforcement for traffic violations, including speeding,reckless driving, 
using your mobile while driving, aiming a weapon, smashed windows, dangling bumper parts and more.
Face real consequences with traffic tickets, losing your driver's license, or having your car impounded.
Speed limits are enforced across the map, challenging you to follow the rules or risk getting caught.

--------------
BANKING SYSTEM
--------------

Deposit Money, Withdraw Money and earn weekly interest in money in your account,
The banking system also has the ability for you to go in debt which will have consequences.
You can earn money in your bank by completing legal activities or jobs.

--------------------------
VEHICLE PERSISTENCE SYSTEM
--------------------------

Your vehicles and their modifications will persist across game saves, saving their location and any customizations you've made.
Lock and unlock your vehicles with ease, adding an extra layer of security to your prized possessions.


